@DATABASE "Hawk Storm +2A"
@NODE "MAIN" "SPECCY POKES - H - Hawk Storm +2A"
@TOC "MAIN"

                   ZX SPECTRUM (SPECCY heheh) POKES - H
                   ====================================

                              Hawk Storm +2A
                              ==============


DESCRIPTION              POKE
===========              ====

@{"Infinite Ammo    " RXS "ADDRESS COMMAND ZXAMPOKE(34880,0)"}       34880,0
@{"Infinite Bombs   " RXS "ADDRESS COMMAND ZXAMPOKE(32197,0)"}       32197,0
@{"Infinite Stryders" RXS "ADDRESS COMMAND ZXAMPOKE(37680,0)"}       37680,0
@{"Infinite Shields " RXS "ADDRESS COMMAND ZXAMPOKE(41906,0)"}       41906,0
@{"Immunity         " RXS "ADDRESS COMMAND ZXAMPOKE(32163,0) zxampoke(35318,0) zxampoke(36616,0) zxampoke(37816,0)"}       32163,0:35318,0:36616,0:37816,0
@{"Barrier Hits = x " RXS "ADDRESS COMMAND ZXAMPOKE(33380,1)"}       33380,x (x= 1-255)
@{"Gun Hits = x     " RXS "ADDRESS COMMAND ZXAMPOKE(33385,1)"}       33385,x (x= 1-255)


                         Change x to whatever value you wish, using
                         the POKE option on the ZXAM GUI. Simply
                         click the button to get the maximum value
                         x can be (usually 255).

                         The "Barrier Hits" and "Gun Hits" POKEs
                         set how many times you have to shoot them
                         to destroy them.

                         I included this POKE in case someone ends
                         up with a snapshot of the +2A version when
                         ZXAM 128 is finally released.

                         This is one of my POKEs. Enjoy!

                         Rastan.
@endnode
